     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d100n3-ptr" id="PJA04d100n3">3</a>
      
   <p>Even good Homer sometimes nods.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d100n4-ptr" id="PJA04d100n4">4</a>
      
